  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❄️ <strong>A Magical Christmas Journey</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an atmospheric holiday adventure across snowy Europe! Cozy markets, ancient towns, and northern landscapes filled with festive spirit await you. Explore historic locations across Europe and Scandinavia, search for hidden objects, solve mini-games, and collect holiday souvenirs to take a piece of winter magic with you. 🎄✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.poster.avif?t=1772654327\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.webm?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.mp4?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>New Features & Engaging Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new object-search mechanics and a variety of fresh mini-games. Explore 30 picturesque locations and tourist attractions created especially for this winter voyage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stroll through Berlin’s Christmas market, visit Santa Claus in Finland, walk across Prague’s snowy Charles Bridge, and uncover even more festive corners of Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skate on ice rinks, travel by train, ship, and airplane, and enjoy a magical route filled with wonder. To succeed, you’ll need attention, logic, and love for details 🎁⛄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.poster.avif?t=1772654327\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.webm?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.mp4?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎅 <strong>The Collector’s Edition includes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 8 extra locations — continue your journey and find our playful raccoon!<br>• 8 new mini-games + 12 bonus puzzles for true fans<br>• Colorful desktop wallpapers<br>• Music player<br>• Album with exclusive postage stamps<br>• 20 Christmas souvenirs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the cozy holiday atmosphere and discover winter Europe as you’ve never seen it before! ❄️🎄✨</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❄️ <strong>A Magical Christmas Journey</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an atmospheric holiday adventure across snowy Europe! Cozy markets, ancient towns, and northern landscapes filled with festive spirit await you. Explore historic locations across Europe and Scandinavia, search for hidden objects, solve mini-games, and collect holiday souvenirs to take a piece of winter magic with you. 🎄✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.poster.avif?t=1772654327\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.webm?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/6908bd2412fe447e82033f33bba79831.mp4?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>New Features & Engaging Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new object-search mechanics and a variety of fresh mini-games. Explore 30 picturesque locations and tourist attractions created especially for this winter voyage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stroll through Berlin’s Christmas market, visit Santa Claus in Finland, walk across Prague’s snowy Charles Bridge, and uncover even more festive corners of Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skate on ice rinks, travel by train, ship, and airplane, and enjoy a magical route filled with wonder. To succeed, you’ll need attention, logic, and love for details 🎁⛄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.poster.avif?t=1772654327\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.webm?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746330/extras/db8339aea9b81f083c32d6f06a847135.mp4?t=1772654327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎅 <strong>The Collector’s Edition includes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 8 extra locations — continue your journey and find our playful raccoon!<br>• 8 new mini-games + 12 bonus puzzles for true fans<br>• Colorful desktop wallpapers<br>• Music player<br>• Album with exclusive postage stamps<br>• 20 Christmas souvenirs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the cozy holiday atmosphere and discover winter Europe as you’ve never seen it before! ❄️🎄✨</p>",
